OL,3,GNEWSCBBC One Scotland broadcasts The
OL,4,COne Show studio output in error
OL,5,
OL,6,FViewers of BBC One Scotland were
OL,7,Funexpectedly presented with output from
OL,8,FThe One Show studio during the opening
OL,9,Fminutes of tonight's BBC News at Six.
OL,11,FSeconds into the opening titles for the
OL,12,FBBC News at Six ` and after the opening
OL,13,Fnetwork and Scottish headlines ` The
OL,14,FOne Show studio was put to air.
OL,16,FPresenters Clara Amfo and Alex Jones
OL,17,Fwere seen and heard chatting with
OL,18,Fmembers of the programme's production
OL,19,Fteam.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
